<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 08:10:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“粉碎哈马斯”与“带他们回家”：以色列人质如何成为丑陋政治游戏中的棋子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/how-israeli-hostages-became-pawns-in-an-ugly-political-game/00000191-75a1-d189-adbb-7dad718a0000</link><description>呼吁释放加沙人质的活动人士感到，这是他们核心民族身份的紧迫性，而以色列右翼则认为，任何协议都将有助于激励哈马斯。如果内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们考虑到这些困境就好了</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 07:32:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/how-israeli-hostages-became-pawns-in-an-ugly-political-game/00000191-75a1-d189-adbb-7dad718a0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么现在与真主党的停火协议对以色列不利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-cease-fire-deal-with-hezbollah-now-is-bad-for-israel/00000191-7412-db7d-a7d7-7c9af4eb0000</link><description>正如国际调解人所希望的那样，将加沙和黎巴嫩的停战协议联系起来，将使主张消除主义的真主党取得宣传胜利，并对以色列的威慑和防御造成危险的影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 05:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-cease-fire-deal-with-hezbollah-now-is-bad-for-israel/00000191-7412-db7d-a7d7-7c9af4eb0000</guid></item><item><title>一个新的危险阶段：以色列与哈马斯未能达成协议将加剧中东地区更广泛冲突的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/failure-to-reach-hostage-deal-risks-wider-iran-hezbollah-response/00000191-769c-db30-a797-7ede7d000000</link><description>美国最近对确保停火的乐观态度可能被夸大了。虽然布林肯的出席确保真主党或伊朗不会在民主党全国代表大会期间对以色列进行报复，但情报显示黎巴嫩武装分子决心很快发动报复袭击。在华盛顿，希望奇迹至少还能再持续一天</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/failure-to-reach-hostage-deal-risks-wider-iran-hezbollah-response/00000191-769c-db30-a797-7ede7d000000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告：以色列对加沙的袭击造成11人死亡；以色列国防军西岸无人机袭击造成三人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-live/white-house-biden-stressed-urgency-of-sealing-gaza-deal-in-conversation-with-netanyahu/00000191-77df-dacb-afb3-ffffd81d0000</link><description>火箭袭击以色列北部时，以色列国防军袭击真主党目标 ■ 拜登在与内塔尼亚胡通话时强调达成加沙协议的“紧迫性” ■ 内塔尼亚胡誓言以色列空军已做好应对以色列北部任何情况的准备 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它击毙了黎巴嫩境内的 IRGC 武装分子和该战斗机喷气式飞机一夜之间杀死了真主党武装分子</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-live/white-house-biden-stressed-urgency-of-sealing-gaza-deal-in-conversation-with-netanyahu/00000191-77df-dacb-afb3-ffffd81d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国以色列人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的父母向《国土报》表示：我们对民主党全国委员会的积极接待感到震惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-to-haaretz-were-overwhelmed-by-positive-reception-at-dnc/00000191-77d8-dc26-a9d7-f7d9ca870001</link><description>乔恩·波林 (Jon Polin) 和雷切尔·戈德堡 (Rachel Goldberg) 的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 于 10 月 7 日被绑架，他们在民主党全国代表大会上发表讲话，高呼“带他们回家”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-to-haaretz-were-overwhelmed-by-positive-reception-at-dnc/00000191-77d8-dc26-a9d7-f7d9ca870001</guid></item><item><title>在民主党全国委员会拒绝给巴勒斯坦裔美国发言人时间后，“不承诺”举行静坐抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</link><description>明尼苏达州州长基思·埃里森（Keith Ellison）直言不讳地批评以色列，他告诉代表们，“卡马拉·哈里斯在加沙问题上正在倾听我们的意见”，随后引发抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 01:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</guid></item><item><title>“现在是时候了”：美国-以色列人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的父母在民主党全国委员会发表讲话，呼吁达成协议以结束痛苦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/addressing-dnc-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-call-for-deal-to-end-to-gaza-agony/00000191-775e-dacb-afb3-ffff01e80000</link><description>乔恩·波林 (Jon Polin) 和雷切尔·戈德堡 (Rachel Goldberg) 的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 于 10 月 7 日被绑架，他们告诉民主党人，“在痛苦的竞争中，没有赢家”。人群中许多人高呼“带他们回家”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 00:14:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/addressing-dnc-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-call-for-deal-to-end-to-gaza-agony/00000191-775e-dacb-afb3-ffff01e80000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普指责舒默是哈马斯成员，并指责民主党导致以色列输掉公关战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-accuses-schumer-of-being-hamas-member-blames-democrats-for-israel-losing-pr-battle/00000191-76ed-d2f3-afdf-7ffd13cf0000</link><description>前总统还对“犹太游说团体”失去影响力表示遗憾，如果这些评论来自对美国公共事务委员会（AIPAC）等组织的民主党批评者，共和党人可能会谴责这些言论为反犹太主义。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 22:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-accuses-schumer-of-being-hamas-member-blames-democrats-for-israel-losing-pr-battle/00000191-76ed-d2f3-afdf-7ffd13cf0000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列组织试图撤销巴勒斯坦记者的艾美奖提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-group-tries-to-get-emmy-nomination-rescinded-from-palestinian-journalist/00000191-7667-dacb-afb3-ffff5ae80000</link><description>Bisan Atef Owda 制作的《来自加沙的 Bisan，我还活着》获得艾美奖提名。一家亲以色列的非营利组织写了一封公开信，称 Owda 与美国指定的恐怖组织 PFLP 有“记录在案的联系”，因此不应被提名</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-group-tries-to-get-emmy-nomination-rescinded-from-palestinian-journalist/00000191-7667-dacb-afb3-ffff5ae80000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在副总统哈里斯的陪同下与内塔尼亚胡通话，敦促加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/president-biden-speaks-with-netanyahu-on-call-joined-by-vp-harris-white-house-says/00000191-7678-db30-a797-7e7a16c90000</link><description>拜登政府高级官员表示，布林肯本周早些时候的言论造成了一种乐观和进步的错误感觉</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:17:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/president-biden-speaks-with-netanyahu-on-call-joined-by-vp-harris-white-house-says/00000191-7678-db30-a797-7e7a16c90000</guid></item><item><title>不要评判人质家属的痛苦，或者他们表达痛苦的方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-21/ty-article/.highlight/dont-judge-the-hostage-families-pain-or-how-they-express-it/00000191-75f8-dc26-a9d7-f5f9daef0000</link><description>当人质家属希望俘虏政治敌人的孩子而不是自己的孩子时，我们应该如何应对？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-21/ty-article/.highlight/dont-judge-the-hostage-families-pain-or-how-they-express-it/00000191-75f8-dc26-a9d7-f5f9daef0000</guid></item><item><title>“政府希望以色列人过于担心自己的安全而忽视民主”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-21/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-hoping-israelis-are-too-worried-about-safety-to-think-about-democracy/00000191-6f18-d43c-af93-ff5820fc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-21/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-hoping-israelis-are-too-worried-about-safety-to-think-about-democracy/00000191-6f18-d43c-af93-ff5820fc0000</guid></item><item><title>谁是布拉德·兰德（Brad Lander），竞选纽约市长的进步犹太人和加沙停火倡导者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-progressive-jew-and-gaza-cease-fire-advocate-running-for-new-york-mayor/00000191-6a3c-deb0-ab91-ffbcd4d40000</link><description>纽约审计长布拉德·兰德 (Brad Lander) 三十年前开始了他的职业生涯，为布鲁克林受压迫的社区发声。现在，他的任务是推翻纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯(Eric Adams)，这场竞选已经受到以色列-加沙战争的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-progressive-jew-and-gaza-cease-fire-advocate-running-for-new-york-mayor/00000191-6a3c-deb0-ab91-ffbcd4d40000</guid></item><item><title>解释：费拉德尔菲和内扎里姆，这两条阻碍加沙和以色列停火的“走廊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-two-corridors-that-are-stymieing-a-gaza-israel-deal/00000191-7500-d2f3-afdf-7dd97ce70000</link><description>哈马斯长期走私武器的费城走廊沿着加沙和埃及边境延伸，而东西向的内扎里姆走廊则允许以色列军队一分为二并控制加沙地带。但哈马斯表示，如果以色列不从两国全面撤军，就不会达成人质/停火协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:55:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-two-corridors-that-are-stymieing-a-gaza-israel-deal/00000191-7500-d2f3-afdf-7dd97ce70000</guid></item><item><title>为寻求谈判突破，哈马斯向真主党施压，要求其加大对以色列的攻击力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-deal-unlikely-hamas-looking-to-hezbollah-to-increase-pressure-on-israel/00000191-7584-d189-adbb-7d8c3cec0000</link><description>以色列、巴勒斯坦、美国和阿拉伯官员都对达成协议的可能性表示悲观，理由是内塔尼亚胡总理不断增加的要求、哈马斯不愿放弃唯一的筹码，以及叶海亚·辛瓦尔希望引发与真主党和伊朗的地区战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-deal-unlikely-hamas-looking-to-hezbollah-to-increase-pressure-on-israel/00000191-7584-d189-adbb-7d8c3cec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争第 320 天：据报道，官员称加沙休战谈判“濒临崩溃”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-320-gaza-truce-talks-on-brink-of-collapse-officials-reportedly-say/00000191-75b5-d8d0-a7bb-fdb573d00000</link><description>参与谈判的消息人士告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡“再次破坏与哈马斯的人质释放/停火协议谈判” ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了约 50 枚火箭，造成一名男子中度受伤 ■ 六个加沙边境社区、人质家庭论坛宣布他们将抵制政府组织的 10 月 7 日大屠杀纪念仪式 ■ 这是战争 320 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-320-gaza-truce-talks-on-brink-of-collapse-officials-reportedly-say/00000191-75b5-d8d0-a7bb-fdb573d00000</guid></item><item><title>巨型鸟类如何在空气稀薄的高空停留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/how-giant-birds-stay-aloft-at-great-heights-where-the-air-is-thin/00000191-7595-daab-a3f3-f59784c50000</link><description>在七英里高的地方，您从喷气式客机的窗户向外望去，与秃鹰四目相对。这种情况非常罕见，但确实发生了。那些秃头美女是怎么呆在上面的？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/how-giant-birds-stay-aloft-at-great-heights-where-the-air-is-thin/00000191-7595-daab-a3f3-f59784c50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列执意要拆散这些乌克兰家庭？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-is-israel-insisting-on-breaking-these-ukrainian-families-up/00000191-7401-dabe-a597-ff2bd1170000</link><description>尽管安娜在乌克兰战争中丧生的丈夫是以色列公民，但她无法在以色列获得合法地位。扎哈尔计划加入以色列国防军，像哥哥一样去加沙服役，但入籍申请未获批准</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:34:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-is-israel-insisting-on-breaking-these-ukrainian-families-up/00000191-7401-dabe-a597-ff2bd1170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前特使称联合国“没有必要，应该从地球上抹去”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-envoy-to-un-calls-it-unnecessary-and-should-be-wiped-off-the-earth/00000191-7557-dc26-a9d7-f5dfb56f0000</link><description>即将离任的以色列驻联合国大使吉拉德·埃尔丹表示，“没有哪个地方比联合国更腐败和道德扭曲了。”他在任期内习惯于发表有争议的花招和言论。他敦促各国团结起来，要求“关闭和解散”联合国</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-envoy-to-un-calls-it-unnecessary-and-should-be-wiped-off-the-earth/00000191-7557-dc26-a9d7-f5dfb56f0000</guid></item><item><title>因哄抬物价受到批评后，以色列航空公司将出售飞往四个目的地的固定价格机票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/following-criticism-el-al-to-sell-fixed-price-tickets-to-four-destinations/00000191-750f-daab-a3f3-f58f07f30000</link><description>该航空公司将运营飞往拉纳卡、迪拜、雅典和维也纳的固定价格航班，以色列人可以在那里转乘飞往其他国家的航班。该决定是在以色列航空公司首席执行官与经济部长尼尔·巴尔卡特交谈后宣布的</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 14:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/following-criticism-el-al-to-sell-fixed-price-tickets-to-four-destinations/00000191-750f-daab-a3f3-f58f07f30000</guid></item></channel></rss>